items.description: The patterned shotgun coat, tailor made fancy pants, silver buckle garden deluxe spurs, metal tipped deluxe relentless boots and silk opulent vest will make you the delight of a paddlewheel riverboat excursion. With the tables humming and the night heavy with the sounds of river insects and music, nod at the dealer, bite on your cigar wit ha smile, take it out of your mouth with knowing satisfaction, blow a prodigious plume of smoke in the air with a chuckle and push your pile of chips into the middle of the table, look at your rival in the eye and say “all in”.

items.description: The demand this season from professional men for a suit that is proper for doing business in town but also an afternoon of hunting, has induced us to present to you this fine assemblage. A fashionable combination of saddle work pants, traditional vest and sharp rambler jacket is paired with preacher’s pride boots and western deluxe spurs, topped off with a rolled derby hat and neat ascot tie. It conveys the ambition of a man that is equally skilled at discussing the nuances of politics as jumping a horse over a fence at considerable speed. No better outfit can be had at this price.

items.description: We bring your attention to one of the finest outfits we have on offer. This beautifully tailored shotgun coat with fancy brass buttons, everyday overshirt, two tone leather shotgun chaps and exquisite tornado boots, plus a stalker hat with accented leather band, all fit and complement each other. The beauty of design, the quality of the material used; it is, in fact, general perfection. For it says the wearer possesses nobility of character, is adroit at the pleasures of the company of woman, sometimes more than one simultaneously.

items.description: All garments are guaranteed exactly as represented. We present to you the leading style in both work and leisure wear today. The long Duster Coat, worsted vest, cotton twill shirt, heavy grade pantaloons and square toed boots and gambler’s style hat are completed with a pair of sleeked leather Cavalry Gloves. Despair may be picturesque, but when one wears an outfit that conveys misery or grievance, they are indeed a burden on society. By all accounts the customers in this line of outfits are men who can exhibit cheerfulness while enduring crushing sorrow.

items.description: Handling over a thousand suits a day, a few patterns stand out as leaders. The Bretagne, made up in a thoroughly first class manner by top tailors, is a favorite among residents of Saint Denis. The Classic Frock Coat, Cuffed Town Pants, metal accented Deluxe Relentless Boots with Vaquero Spurs and Stand-Collar Overshirt are complimented by the neatly brimmed Western Hat. Those who have no social responsibility in life will undoubtedly pass over this elegant, stylish suit that is equally at comfort entertaining in a parlor as it is amusing players at a poker table as they throw down a card, bankrupting their foes of their livelihood and ability to meet their obligations to civilization.

items.description: Following is a description of our improved line of cowpuncher outfits. The black cotton overshirt compliments the fancy striped vest, denim pantaloons, and black boots. The leather chaps are decorated with a bit of fringe, the hat ornamented with a leather band, shielding the wearer’s eyes from the noonday sun. The immense amount of business we are doing in our outfits department and continual growing demand is testament to our dedication to this business and the cheerful disregard of recent history. Especially the shirt factory fire and the dozens of our employees who perished, giving their lives so that you could place an order today. But that’s life, and you move on, hopefully better dressed.

items.description: This ensemble is smart in every manner, from the duster coat, flat cap, stylish button up fancy pants, and preacher’s pride boots. It extolls the graces and virtues of one who shuns a desultory life, and should he hear someone detailing repetition of his scandals in hushed tones, he would march up and strike them about the face. A man who rarely ruminates on his poor state of hosiery casts gloom on all around him, for the improperly dressed carry a cloud over themselves. Place a large order, throw out your old mottled apparel, and join your neighbors arm in arm, dancing gaily on at this universal vanity, as lives are changed for the better by the fine purveyors at Wheeler and Rawson.

items.description: The maroon rambler jacket is accented by a smart opulent vest and pinstriped saddle work pants, completed with hand tooled deluxe quickdraw boots. It conveys a smart but slightly rugged demeanor, someone who can not only cipher mathematics but change a wagon wheel if need. We have spoken with a great many men from all areas of the country who have found that the simple act of wearing this outfit has caused women to have the vapors and fall lifeless at their feet.

items.description: You no doubt belong to a class of persons who are not affluent, otherwise you would have a servant read this catalogue and order for you while finer things such as golf or writing memoirs are pursued. We strive to make the world’s goods affordable to those who may lack refinement but seek to put on the airs of belonging to a class they do not. In that manner, we call your attention to this handsome and stunning assemblage. With a long Shotgun Coat, light summer vest, pinstriped pantaloons with rolled cuffs, square toed boots and laundered shirt, it is topped off with a hat whose band matches the vest. The workmanship is first class.

items.description: We draw your attention to our line of outfits featuring a fancy striped Everyday Overshirt accentuated by a fancy patterned Opulent Vest. Complimented with Work Pants and Preacher’s Boots, it is faultless in fit and handsome in every detail and finish, suitable for a garden party or bare knuckle brawl. Our collection of expert tailors, men of fashion, seamstresses and needle workers spend long hours assembling these outfits for you. Many, quite candidly, have inquired why you have yet to express your gratefulness by placing an order for one or several right away.

items.description: This well made, graceful and attractive ensemble has long been a favorite of Irish settlers who moved to New York City and, later, Blackwater and surrounding environs. The green fancy patterned French Dress Shirt, cuffed Worsted Coat with patterned stripes, beige Fancy Pants and lace up Sportsman’s Boots set the tone of a professional gentleman who has adapted to the local ways of this new country, yet can at times, when enjoying a libation, adopt the surly, rapacious demeanor of his ancestors. This outfit is truly the evolution of our genius in clothing concerns, and worth every expense.

items.description: The Business of moving livestock, branding, dehorning, chasing down mavericks and castrating animals requires a specific outfit. Complete with Duster Coat, Shotgun Chaps, Gerden Spurs and a sensible Military Scout Hat, we sell more cowpuncher attire than any catalogue concern on earth. Working cattle is a serious affair and, as in most matters in life, the clothes make the man. All garments are guaranteed exactly as they are represented. We endeavour to hire artists that perfectly depict the look and feel of each garment so that upon arrival there is no embarrassment. Should you feel otherwise, return your order, and we will chastise them appropriately.

items.description: With a combination frock coat, stovepipe preacher’s pride boots, studded stenger deluxe spurs, pinstriped work pants and fancy bright patterned opulent vest, this outfit will largely be worn by very good dressers. Premeditated coordination of an outfit is an expression of a refined civilization. Fashion comes from without, civility comes from within, and this suit conveys a man who has the very finest manners, is of refinement an taste, but at the slightest affront can flip a switch and study you with unwavering and steely determination, leaping out of a chair and fixing a knife to your throat in a blur.

items.description: A man’s manners are his fortune, and while a penniless beggar may be kind and courteous, he is still far too destitute to enjoy the finer things, such as these outfits, which are beyond exception. This one in particular conveys the rugged yet refined countenance of a man who is equally adept at castrating a horse as he is felling a tree, sawing the limbs, and fashioning a home for which to someday perform coitus indoors. The boots are handstitched, the pants tough for outdoor work. The striped patterned shirt with white collar is best suited for he who rolls up his sleeves, puts on leather gloves, and gets to the matter at hand.

items.description: To show our confidence in this ensemble we make the following offer: We will ship it by express on a 20 day trial to any freight office on a railroad within 400 miles of our headquarters. Once it is taken out of the box, the oiled leather boots put on with gaiters, the grey wool vest buttoned, the long leather coat pulled over each arm and the riding gloves slid over each hand, the wearer will size himself up in a mirror. He’ll slide his fingers across the brim of the frayed hat and chuckle at how far we have come, from when men dressed in skins, ate roots, made homes in caves and shared fires.

items.description: In his later years, Josiah Blackwater was known to work and entertain callers to his ranch in this outfit. With a patterned traditional vest, pinstriped Everyday Shirt, Everyday Pants and exquisite two-tone leather Roper Boots and stitched Riding Gloves, he performed chores while delighting others with the tales of the unpardonable offenses of northerners in Congress. This catalogue is replete with unbiased quotations from honorable customers overflowing with sincere elation, pride, gratification and glee upon receiving their order.

items.description: To alleviate the grinding fatigue of working in dirty, humid, bustling cities and outposts such as Valentine, we offer this custom made outfit, sure to delight on days when the mercury is in excess of 90 degrees. With long coat, open neck shirt and fancy vest, it is completed by worsted patterned trousers, Riding Boots, and Plantation Hat for beating the rays of the sun. It is for the refined working gentleman, who does not often make comparisons of a foe to a drooling invalid and only reaches into his quiver of vulgarities when absolutely necessary. A dapper demeanor is not only pleasing when conducting business, it is a necessity in a society in order to regulate intercourse among people that society could do without.

items.description: We furnish many styles of clothing, with few reaching the dapper, fine cut, and clean look of this noble ensemble. Inspired by the businessmen of Rhodes and the deep family traditions that exist there, the long coat is ornamented with shiny silver buttons. The fancy patterned bosom of the shirt is matched by the wool trousers and brown Preacher’s Pride Boots. Topped off by a Derby hat, it is one of our finer outfits, and 75,000 of them have sold without a just complaint. Most complaints we receive are preposterous, so much so that we laugh upon reading them and toss them promptly in the bin.

With jeans, wide brimmed big valley hat, classic frock coat, and everyday shirt with a fashionable pattern of neat stripes, it is one of the most stylish working wear outfits we have on offer. This ensemble communicates success, and success affords you to secure additional success.

items.description: The marked success we have had the past season with this outfit confirms that our patrons prefer the bold, rugged, yet refined look. The Classic Frock Coat, striped vest and wool spring weight pantaloons are finished with studded two-tone boots. We take this opportunity to remind you that carelessness in measuring will ruin any outfit. If you are unfamiliar with measuring, visit a local tailor under the auspices of having them make you a suit, get a fitting, and then take the measurements he’s written down out of his hand and walk out the door with a sneer.

With the knee high Preacher’s Boots, Everyday Pants, cotton Everyday Shirt and fancy pattern green Opulent Vest, this is the attire of one who works hard, respects his elders and knows it is rude to whistle in the presence of the elderly, lifts his hat and gives way to strangers.

items.description: A prominent feature in our clothing department is this smartly assembled outfit suitable for taciturn laborers engaged in colder weather livestock work. Featuring a wool lined Scout Jacket, oiled leather Shotgun Chaps and Sleeked Riding Boots, it is the preferred attire for roping an unpliable, inharmonious member of the herd, wrestling the struggling beast to the ground, looking it in the eye and grunting “I will end you” through clenched teeth as you hogtie it and come to a mutual understanding of who is the governor here.

items.description: One of the best and largest manufacturers of woolens that exists in this republic supplies us with these wonderful garments. The fancy cotton worsted patterned vest with brass buttons sits snugly under a neat long wool coat with form fitting wool trousers and lace-up leather boots. We service customers of varying aptitudes, some of refined tastes, who are men of letters, and others who point at this catalogue and grunt, incapable of manners or finding work beyond smashing rocks together. It is of no distinction to us – as long as a person is ambulatory enough to sign a crude “X” on a bill of receipt at the freight depot and pay the chit, it matters not.

items.description: The silver rush of 1858 brought many a miner throughout mountainous regions of the United States. The famed Millesani Mine in Big Valley was abandoned after the Coinage Act in the 1870s favored a gold standard rather than silver. This notable outfit remembers the customary garb of the miners who frequented the saloons and shops of Strawberry between shifts. Wheeler and Rawson is having a splendid business in this line. The quality and munificence of our operation is without question.

items.description: This ready to wear outfit stands out in our clothing department, which has grown to such proportions that it now encompasses several warehouses, due to our tradition of giving customers exceptional value. For we provide clothing to both the man who lives in a wretched shanty at the edge of a corn field as well as the man that rents him that shanty and likely retires each evening to cognac and cigars while studying the world’s musings by firelight. We call your attention to this carefully assembled outfit, comprised of a sturdy tail coat, all wool worsted pantaloons, striped shirt, Preacher’s Pride Boots and hat suitable for both work and recreation.

items.description: A high grade outfit made of the best materials, the Bulldogger is handsome in design and first class in every respect. The trousers are heavyweight material and prevent chafing. With cotton overshirt, wide-brimmed hat, and pinstriped vest, the outfit also features Cavalry Gloves, Boots and wrapped leather gaiters that protect when roping a calf and also prevent getting hung up when bareback riding an unruly bronc or bull. He may get thrown, but he has a braver heart and a stouter spirit than most, shunning nebulous ideas of equality and fairness, for he dons the clothing of a man that knows freedom burns bright, as long as you set fire to it yourself.

Mixed-matched suits are very stylish and increasingly popular among those less inclined to have extra silver available for apparel. Gone are the days where such attire was assumed to be only donned by delinquents with soiled tempers and trousers. Inequalities of fortune are inevitable, and we serve to provide to all levels of nobility of character.

items.description: This outfit services gentlemen the country over, working stock yards and oil fields, railroads and freight depots. The long coat shields from the elements, the plaid pants are from our most popular line. Combined with Riding Boots, grey union shirt and leather banded hat, this ensemble will be found worn by him that requires the leading style but wants more for his money, a man at ease with hard work and the respite that deservedly follows. Yes, his name does fall into unfortunate gossip. His faults and foibles are literally laid out on his sleeve.
